---
title: Cal Smart Lemon-Pepper Pork Tenderloin with Fresh Salad
description: Inspired by the flavours of classic Greek cuisine, this Cal Smart dish pairs juicy lemon-pepper pork tenderloin with the timeless favourite Greek-style salad and creamy tzatziki. Happy eating!

